text:
As part of the inspection,
I'll treat you to something you like.

Then, if you don't mind......
I'll have a Targyibonbon, please.

Thank you very much!
I'll get it ready, so please wait a moment.

Targy...?
What did you order, Madoka?

Here you goー! It's packed with lots of fruits,
so be careful when you carry it♪

......! It's a strawberry parfait
But it's huge...... Can you finish it all by yourself?

N-No!
I'm just worried if it's too much for you......
